<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Langforums</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav>
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <%= link_to current_user.email, main_app.edit_user_registration_path %>
      | <%= link_to "Sign out", main_app.destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete %>
      <% if current_user.forem_admin %>
      | <%= link_to "Administrate", forem.admin_root_url %>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to "Sign up", main_app.new_user_registration_path %>
      | <%= link_to "Sign in", main_app.new_user_session_path %>
    <% end %>
  </nav>
</header>

<p><em>Our much-beloved HTLAL site is having problems.  I've temporary set
up this forum so we can discuss what's going on and what to do next.  See
the posts on this forum for more details. You're welcome to sign up and
post!  <b>-emk</b> (a HTLAL user)</em></p>

<% if notice %>
<p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
<% end %>
<% if alert %>
<p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
<% end %>

<%= yield %>

</body>
</html>
